---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure | ProofLabs"
  description="Learn how ProofLabs earns revenue and maintains editorial independence."
>
  <div class="container-custom" style="padding: 8rem 0 6rem;">
    <div style="max-width: 48rem; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #111827;">
        Affiliate Disclosure
      </h1>
      
      <div style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #374151;">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;">
          Last Updated: March 14, 2026
        </p>
        
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; color: #111827;">
          How We Make Money
        </h2>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          ProofLabs may earn a commission when you click on links to credit card offers and subsequently apply for or are approved for a credit card. These affiliate commissions help support our research and editorial operations.
        </p>
        
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; color: #111827;">
          Editorial Independence
        </h2>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          Our reviews, rankings, and recommendations are determined by our editorial team using our published <a href="/methodology" style="color: #0284c7; text-decoration: underline;">methodology</a>. Affiliate commission rates do not influence our reviews or rankings.
        </p>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          We may feature cards from affiliate partners more prominently, but all cards we review meet our editorial standards regardless of affiliate status.
        </p>
        
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; color: #111827;">
          Accuracy & Updates
        </h2>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          We strive to maintain accurate, up-to-date information about credit card offers, rates, and terms. However, credit card issuers may change offers at any time. We recommend verifying all details directly with the card issuer before applying.
        </p>
        
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; color: #111827;">
          Your Trust Matters
        </h2>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          We take our responsibility to readers seriously. Our goal is to provide objective, data-driven analysis that helps you make informed credit card decisions. Affiliate revenue enables us to offer this service for free while maintaining quality and independence.
        </p>
        
        <div style="background: #eff6ff; border-left: 4px solid #0284c7; padding: 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; border-radius: 0.5rem;">
          <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; color: #0369a1;">
            Questions about our disclosure policy? <a href="/contact" style="color: #0284c7; text-decoration: underline;">Contact us</a> for more information.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
